{"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"platforms":["iOS","iPadOS","Mac Catalyst"],"languages":["occ"],"tokens":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"@property"},{"kind":"text","text":" ("},{"kind":"keyword","text":"nonatomic"},{"kind":"text","text":", "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"readonly"},{"kind":"text","text":") "},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:@E@MLNOfflinePackState","kind":"typeIdentifier","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflinePackState","text":"MLNOfflinePackState"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"state"},{"kind":"text","text":";"}]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"content":[{"text":"Discussion","level":2,"type":"heading","anchor":"discussion"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The state of an inactive or completed pack is computed lazily and is set to"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflinePackState\/MLNOfflinePackStateUnknown"},{"type":"text","text":" by default. To request the pack’s status, use"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"-requestProgress"},{"type":"text","text":" method. To get notified when the state becomes known and"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"when it changes, observe KVO change notifications on this pack’s "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"state"},{"type":"text","text":" key"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"path. Alternatively, you can add an observer for"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflinePackProgressChangedNotification"},{"type":"text","text":"s about this pack that come from the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"default notification center."}],"type":"paragraph"}],"kind":"content"}],"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnofflinepack\/state"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}]}],"metadata":{"fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"state"}],"modules":[{"name":"MapLibre"}],"externalID":"c:objc(cs)MLNOfflinePack(py)state","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"state","kind":"identifier"}],"title":"state","role":"symbol","roleHeading":"Instance Property","symbolKind":"property"},"sections":[],"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflinePack\/state","interfaceLanguage":"occ"},"abstract":[{"text":"The pack’s current state.","type":"text"}],"kind":"symbol","schemaVersion":{"patch":0,"minor":3,"major":0},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflinePack"]]},"references":{"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNOfflinePack/state":{"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnofflinepack\/state","abstract":[{"text":"The pack’s current state.","type":"text"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflinePack\/state","title":"state","role":"symbol","type":"topic","kind":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"state","kind":"identifier"}]},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNOfflinePack":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflinePack","kind":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnofflinepack","type":"topic","title":"MLNOfflinePack","abstract":[{"text":"An ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflinePack"},{"text":" represents a collection of resources necessary for viewing","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"a region offline to a local database.","type":"text"}],"role":"symbol","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNOfflinePack"}]},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNOfflinePackState/MLNOfflinePackStateUnknown":{"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnofflinepackstate\/mlnofflinepackstateunknown","abstract":[{"text":"It is unknown whether the pack is inactive, active, or complete.","type":"text"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflinePackState\/MLNOfflinePackStateUnknown","title":"MLNOfflinePackStateUnknown","role":"symbol","type":"topic","kind":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"MLNOfflinePackStateUnknown","kind":"identifier"}]},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre":{"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Powerful, free and open-source mapping toolkit with full control over data sources and styling."}],"title":"MapLibre","role":"collection","type":"topic","kind":"symbol"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNOfflineStorage":{"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnofflinestorage","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflineStorage","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"MLNOfflineStorage implements a singleton (shared object) that manages offline"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"packs and ambient caching. All of this class’s instance methods are asynchronous,"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"reflecting the fact that offline resources are stored in a database. The shared"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"object maintains a canonical collection of offline packs in its "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"packs"},{"type":"text","text":" property."}],"title":"MLNOfflineStorage","role":"symbol","type":"topic","kind":"symbol","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNOfflineStorage"}]},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNOfflinePackProgressChangedNotification":{"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnofflinepackprogresschangednotification","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflinePackProgressChangedNotification","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Posted by the shared "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflineStorage","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" object when an "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflinePack","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"object’s progress changes. The progress may change due to a resource being"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"downloaded or because the pack discovers during the download that more"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"resources are required for offline viewing. This notification is posted"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"whenever any field in the "},{"code":"progress","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" property changes."}],"title":"MLNOfflinePackProgressChangedNotification","role":"symbol","type":"topic","kind":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"MLNOfflinePackProgressChangedNotification","kind":"identifier"}]},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNOfflinePackState":{"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnofflinepackstate","abstract":[{"text":"The state an offline pack is currently in.","type":"text"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflinePackState","title":"MLNOfflinePackState","role":"symbol","type":"topic","kind":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"MLNOfflinePackState","kind":"identifier"}]}}}